Patrick Edward Purdy, AKA Eddie Purdy West, 24, had blue eyes and blond hair.
Through third grade he attended Cleveland Elementary School in Stockton, California,  where he killed five children on Tuesday.
His mother, divorced and remarried, took him  and moved away.
His father was killed by a car in 1981.
Purdy dropped out of high  school, took welding classes, then drifted around the country searching for work.
In the  LA area he was arrested on prostitution, marijuana, and weapons charges, and for robbery  and receiving stolen property.
He attempted suicide in jail.
He had white supremacist  leanings and was described as dangerous and mildly retarded. 
